OL,3,CPlaid Cymru politician Owen John
OL,4,CThomas has died at the age of 84
OL,6,FThe founder of Clwb Ifor Bach in
OL,7,FCardiff and former Assembly Member has
OL,8,Fdied at the age of 84.
OL,10,FThe politician served as a Assembly
OL,11,FMember (AM) for the South Wales
OL,12,FCentral region from 1999 to 2007.
OL,14,FMr Thomas served as Plaid Cymru's
OL,15,Fspokesman for culture, the Welsh
OL,16,Flanguage and sport during his time in
OL,17,Fthe Assembly.
