OL,4,CThomas has died at the age of 84
OL,6,FHe wrote a book on the Welsh language
OL,7,Fin Cardiff and helped found the music
OL,8,Fvenue on Womanby Street known as Clwb
OL,9,FIfor Bach or, to generations of
OL,10,Fstudents, the Welsh club.
OL,12,FIn 2013, Mr Thomas was diagnosed with
OL,13,Fdementia.
