OL,3,CPlaid Cymru politician Owen John
OL,4,CThomas has died at the age of 84
OL,6,FHis son Hywel, who worked for him
OL,7,Fduring his time in the Assembly, and
OL,8,Fsaid: "He loved Wales, its people,
OL,9,Flanguage, and culture with a passion.
OL,10,FHe was driven by a desire to see Wales
OL,11,Ffreed from the constraints of
OL,12,FWestminster to determine its own
OL,13,Faffairs.
OL,15,F"All he ever wanted for his country
OL,16,Fwas fairness and the powers to lift
OL,17,Fthe people of Wales out of poverty and
OL,18,Fgive them a fighting chance of a
OL,19,Fbetter future. Progress was slow,
OL,20,Fletter after letter, inch by inch but
OL,21,Fhe kept going and never gave up...
