OL,3,CPlaid Cymru politician Owen John
OL,4,CThomas has died at the age of 84
OL,6,F"My father never tired of walking
OL,7,Fthrough the streets and arcades of
OL,8,FCardiff city centre, stopping and
OL,9,Fchatting to people along the way `
OL,10,Fsometimes frustratingly so for me and
OL,11,Fmy siblings. But the reward for our
OL,12,Fpatience was a visit to the
OL,13,FSarsaparilla Bar in Morgan's Arcade.
OL,14,FThere, we would sit on the high
OL,15,Fbarstools at the counter sipping our
OL,16,FSarsaparilla and Burdock feeling like
OL,17,Fgrownups."
