OL,3,CPlaid Cymru politician Owen John
OL,4,CThomas has died at the age of 84
OL,6,FLeader of Plaid Cymru, Rhun ap
OL,7,FIorwerth MS, extended his deepest
OL,8,Fcondolences to the family and friends
OL,9,Fof Owen John Thomas.
OL,11,FHe stated: "We remember him as a
OL,12,Fformidable campaigner and tireless
OL,13,Fadvocate for the Welsh language and
OL,14,FWelshness in Cardiff.
OL,16,F"He made a significant contribution
OL,17,Fnot only to his community but also to
OL,18,FPlaid Cymru.
