OL,3,CPlaid Cymru politician Owen John
OL,4,CThomas has died at the age of 84
OL,6,F"From campaigning for the rights of
OL,7,FAllied Steel and Wire pensioners and
OL,8,FWelsh Language Education in the
OL,9,Fcapital to playing a part in shaping
OL,10,FPlaid Cymru's strategy after the 1979
OL,11,Freferendum - he made a lasting
OL,12,Fcontribution to Welsh politics, both
OL,13,Flocally and nationally."
OL,15,FFormer ASW employees and pensions
OL,16,Fcampaigners Phil Jones and John Benson
OL,17,Fsaid Mr Thomas would always have the
OL,18,Futmost respect of everyone involved in
OL,19,Ftheir campaign.
