OL,3,CPlaid Cymru politician Owen John
OL,4,CThomas has died at the age of 84
OL,6,FHe said: "He did so much for us
OL,7,Fregarding our pension miscarriage of
OL,8,Fjustice, we at ASW will always be
OL,9,Fproud to have known a legend of a man
OL,10,Fwho helped so many, a man and a
OL,11,Fpolitician who could always hold his
OL,12,Fhead high."
OL,14,FWelsh Labour MP for Cardiff Central,
OL,15,FJo Stevens tweeted on X (formerly
OL,16,FTwitter) : Very sad news from the
OL,17,FThomas family about Owen John Thomas,
OL,18,Fthe founder of our iconic Cardiff
OL,19,FCentral live music venue.
